data.subject: The perfect Anti-American Storm
data.message: A new Treatment that deals with the Tea Party and how they gained political power through what is called Precinct Committeeman Person/Process/Chairman... Not to forget the Koch Brothers and the Supreme Courts/ Citizens United. A peak into how these Treasonous actions impact us all. The Perfect Anti-American Storm. Any Input is welcome (please know your homework and know what your talking about. No haters allowed). Be a truth seeker and donate your opinion and receive a credit on the real of this yet to be created body of work.
